sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User (UI/BFF)
    participant P as auth-api (:7011)
    participant D as DynamoDB (banned)
    participant R as Redis
    participant M as comms-api
    participant C as customer-api

    Note over U,C: Request — always 200, no enumeration
    U->>P: POST /v1/otp/request
    P->>D: banned-customer gate
    P->>R: SETNX cooldown (429 + Retry-After on conflict)
    P->>R: store 6-digit code, 5-min TTL
    P-->>U: 200 OK
    P-)M: async bounded email send

    Note over U,C: Verify
    U->>P: POST /v1/otp/verify
    P->>R: INCR attempts (cap 5 → 429)
    P->>R: constant-time compare + SetNX redemption claim
    P->>C: resolve user by email
    alt no account
        C-->>P: not found
        P-->>U: 401 (never email-as-sub)
    else lookup error
        C-->>P: error
        P-->>U: 503
    else resolved
        C-->>P: bare uuid
        P-->>U: 30-min access (otp:verified) — no refresh
    end
